OL,6,FA mother and father forced their young
OL,7,Fdaughter to use a wheelchair for four
OL,8,Fyears in a benefits scam.
OL,10,FThe girl, who was aged seven when the
OL,11,Fabuse started, was also made to attend
OL,12,Fnumerous needless medical appointments
OL,13,Fand was kept in hospital unnecessarily.
OL,15,FA court heard she suffered bullying
OL,16,Fand serious psychological harm because
OL,17,Fof the "gratuitous degradation" of
OL,18,Fbeing forced to use the wheelchair.
