OL,6,FThe cruelty was part of a scam by her
OL,7,Fparents, Louise and Martin Law, to
OL,8,Fobtain a mobility car and disability
OL,9,Fallowance payments.JLouise Law, 50, of
OL,10,FHarvest Way in Rawcliffe Bridge near ,
OL,11,Fadmitted an offence of child cruelty
OL,12,Fat .
OL,14,FHer ex-husband, Martin Law, 54,
OL,15,Fformerly of Marshfield Road in Goole,
OL,16,Fwas ruled unfit to enter a plea, but a
OL,17,Fjury found that he committed an act of
OL,18,Fchild cruelty.
