OL,6,FThe court heard that the girl suffered
OL,7,F"far-reaching consequences" and missed
OL,8,Fout on "normal childhood experiences"
OL,9,Fbecause of non-existent illnesses she
OL,10,Fwas supposedly suffering from.JLouise
OL,11,FReevell, prosecuting, said that the
OL,12,Fcruelty happened between 2012 and 2017.
