OL,6,FThe girl was put into foster care at
OL,7,Fthe age of 12.JMrs Reevell added: "At
OL,8,Fthis stage, overnight, she appeared to
OL,9,Fmake a miraculous recovery and did not
OL,10,Frequire a wheelchair. She stopped
OL,11,Ftaking medication and started behaving
OL,12,Flike a normal, healthy child.
OL,14,F"She was able to run up and down
OL,15,Fstairs. She went on to join the Army
OL,16,Fcadets. She did normal activities at
OL,17,Fschool.
OL,19,F"At no point while she was in foster
OL,20,Fcare did she suffer any pain or
OL,21,Ftiredness.
