OL,6,FA consultant psychiatrist said the
OL,7,Fgirl "continues to experience
OL,8,Fnightmares" and struggles with
OL,9,Ffeelings of "overwhelming and deep
OL,10,Fshame".JMrs Reevell told the court:
OL,11,F"It was serious psychological harm for
OL,12,Fher. There were prolonged and multiple
OL,13,Fincidents of serious cruelty. There
OL,14,Fwas gratuitous degradation, making her
OL,15,Fuse a wheelchair for four years and
OL,16,Fdeliberate disregard for her welfare."
