OL,6,FDale Brook, mitigating for Louise Law,
OL,7,Fsaid: "There is some optimism for the
OL,8,Ffuture but this is prolonged or
OL,9,Fmultiple incidents of cruelty, not
OL,10,Fgratuitous degradation of a victim or
OL,11,Fsadistic behaviour."
