OL,6,FThe court heard that Martin Law had
OL,7,Fbeen convicted of two domestic
OL,8,Fviolence offences against his wife.
OL,9,F"This was a toxic and wholly troubled
OL,10,Fmarriage," Mr Brook said.JJudge Kate
OL,11,FRayfield said there had been "far-
OL,12,Freaching consequences" of the
OL,13,Foffending and the couple had put their
OL,14,Fdaughter's welfare last.J"You caused
OL,15,Fher significant harm over a long
OL,16,Fperiod of time," she said.
OL,18,F"There was serious psychological harm
OL,19,Fto her and there still is."
